From: Wyze3306 <remy.grisollet@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 19:15:16 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] winegdk: native5 Xbox and complete file picker runtime

---

diff --git a/dlls/windows.storage/Makefile.in b/dlls/windows.storage/Makefile.in
